{"tid":413764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國有班人覺得連狗失勢，就係咁吹奏紅登","createTime":"2017-09-25T16:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T04:36:07.000Z","uid":52023,"like":27,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af8d65f37b03ed4fc45d29ac6aa2424e8d874965","tid":413764,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"之前有人貼過張圖 <br />\n紅登三成access 嚟自中國<br />\n根本同上香討冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當初林狗ban 人ban 得咁撚開心<br />\n個ser 廢俾人屌撚咗十年都不聞不問<br />\n後尾啲仆街廣告仲要有聲<br />\n嗰陣唔係hkg+我都唔會連到上高登<br />\n<br />\nhkgolden 有十年八載廣告錢就照袋 用戶意見接受 態度照舊<br />\n咁都可以有班傻仔出嚟吹捧話人知自己係狗<br />\n真係諗唔透邊度養班奶閪狗出嚟<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講咩188<br />\n一蚊都唔會俾hkg+以外嘅香港forum apps<br />\n<br />\n就算連狗今次收皮都唔撚輪到上你hkgolden <br />\n好心林狗同佢班奶閪狗自動收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac808bbc975ba215a55fc71b460a0141b93a32a","tid":413764,"uid":41245,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:15:51.000Z","msg":"我只知想畀就畀，唔想畀就唔畀<br />\n唔知有咩問題<br />\n唔係必需嘅<br />\n同埋市場唔得就要減價<br />\n根本唔洗你地呱呱叫<br />\n呱呱叫只顯得你地真係低質（有point都算，有啲走去賴連登多低質用戶，你咪其中一個囉屌）"},{"pid":"22ffaeb4e7deebc1a310112938a29341fdbb4562","tid":413764,"uid":52023,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:17:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我只知想畀就畀，唔想畀就唔畀<br />\n唔知有咩問題<br />\n唔係必需嘅<br />\n同埋市場唔得就要減價<br />\n根本唔洗你地呱呱叫<br />\n呱呱叫只顯得你地真係低質（有point都算，有啲走去賴連登多低質用戶，你咪其中一個囉屌）</blockquote><br />\n喺呢邊屌林狗仲多負皮過屌連狗<br />\n我係咪上錯壇<br />\n咁鍾意林狗點解啲人唔返去奶閪<br />\n仲留喺度同我哋啲低質會員生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017a26eea8fdeec8ed32b077fda79f9d0354cffc","tid":413764,"uid":11980,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:26:16.000Z","msg":"傻仔先返高登"},{"pid":"ae420e93bdcd0215484582fe5cbf9a90305e7708","tid":413764,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:27:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傻仔先返高登</blockquote><br />\n沙清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e0093f42b7dc1becffd7441b5385c01466bcbd","tid":413764,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:27:52.000Z","msg":"呢度點差都唔會返高登<br />\n最多兩邊都唔上"},{"pid":"af69223ed5dfabb6f875233da66a809691ab535e","tid":413764,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:31:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度點差都唔會返高登<br />\n最多兩邊都唔上</blockquote><br />\n香港網民啲質素邊到都係噉㗎啦<br />\n連高登已經叫少五毛<br />\n但如果連登低質<br />\n高登都唔會有咩分別<br />\n一嚟之前已經走晒啲人<br />\n二嚟係喺連登開嗰陣，高登都已經好低質，依家唔會突然高質返<br />\n走乜鬼丫唉"},{"pid":"d4f55ed5266e7732c69e0ba98798ffd1824ca0ae","tid":413764,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:32:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度點差都唔會返高登<br />\n最多兩邊都唔上</blockquote><br />\n間唔中都留意吓啲新壇 <br />\n不過而家好似興telegram group/ig型式仲多過傳統論壇"},{"pid":"f1a60a6531ce01ebeab9af56794f48fe12a0bd11","tid":413764,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T16:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e296098d232d57b4b931b534899f77870fd0df","tid":413764,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42c788ada5ac972b4f7203a9fa268a943736dca","tid":413764,"uid":17111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:53:34.000Z","msg":"似係打手黎，好似連登岩岩開果時咁有堆人又係係咁多角度中傷lihkg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdd6a10e65b30b42ffcac4be6220731c71ca380","tid":413764,"uid":52023,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T04:06:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似係打手黎，好似連登岩岩開果時咁有堆人又係係咁多角度中傷lihkg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g